ProcessEntity.Note:
This component is an UI component to list the future transfers / payments.

 

This component allows the user to view and list the future transfers / payments.

 

Input Parameters: Selected account details, Accounts list, Customer no and OrderType.

 

Output Parameters: Selected Payment order

 

This component depends on transfer / payment component in-order to edit the same.
